Deliver the box

Deliver the box is a game made for VimJam2: boss VimJam 2: Boss [8 Bits to Infinity] it is a parkour type game where the player need to go from building to building delivering the boxes while his boss is giving instruction to him like how to play and other so be sure to play the game and please be sure to left opinion on the comment section thank you for visiting the page
